% 32527783 
@Article{pmid32527783,
   Author="Tracey, A.  and Foster, J. M.  and Paulini, M.  and Grote, A.  and Mattick, J.  and Tsai, Y. C.  and Chung, M.  and Cotton, J. A.  and Clark, T. A.  and Geber, A.  and Holroyd, N.  and Korlach, J.  and Libro, S.  and Lustigman, S.  and Michalski, M. L.  and Rogers, M. B.  and Twaddle, A.  and Dunning Hotopp, J. C.  and Berriman, M.  and Ghedin, E. ",
